> Question

* Given an array nums of size n, return the majority element

```txt
Input: [3,2,3]
Output: 3
```

> Solutino

* Boyer-Moore Voting Algorithm

{% endtab %}
{% tab title='LC_169.cpp' %}

```cpp
// Time : O(N)
int majorityElement(vector<int>& nums) {
  int counter = 0, majority;
  for (int num : nums) {
    if (!counter)
      majority = num;
    counter += num == majority ? 1 : -1;
  }
  return majority;
}
```

